### How many built-in functions are there?

Python 3 provides **around 70 built-in functions** (the exact count can vary slightly between Python versions). You can see them all by running:

```python
import builtins

print(dir(builtins))
```

This lists all built-in functions, exceptions, and other built-in names available in your Python installation.
